OL,3,CMan arrested over murder of 24-year-
OL,4,Cold woman in double stabbing
OL,6,FA man has been arrested over the
OL,7,Fmurder of a 24-year-old woman in west
OL,8,FLondon, police said.
OL,10,FOfficers found the woman with stab
OL,11,Finjuries after being called to a
OL,12,Fproperty on Uxbridge Road, Hayes, on
OL,13,FSunday morning.
OL,15,FA man, aged in his 20s, was found
OL,16,Foutside the property with stab
OL,17,Finjuries, with police awaiting an
OL,18,Fupdate on his condition.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/5
