PN,37702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1784033311
OL,3,CMan arrested over murder of 24-year-
OL,4,Cold woman in double stabbing
OL,6,FA Metropolitan Police spokesman said
OL,7,Fofficers quickly located a 44-year-old
OL,8,Fman matching the suspect's description
OL,9,Fnearby.
OL,11,FHe was arrested on suspicion of murder
OL,12,Fand possession of a bladed article in
OL,13,Fa public place.
OL,15,FThe arrested man was taken to hospital
OL,16,Fwith injuries believed to be caused
OL,17,Ffrom jumping from a window.
OL,19,FLondon Ambulance Service also attended
OL,20,Fthe incident following the emergency
OL,21,Fcall at 7.55am.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/5
