OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1784033311
OL,3,CMan arrested over murder of 24-year-
OL,4,Cold woman in double stabbing
OL,6,FDespite the efforts of emergency
OL,7,Fservices, the woman was pronounced
OL,8,Fdead at the scene.
OL,10,FDetective Chief Inspector Allam
OL,11,FBhangoo said: "This is a shocking
OL,12,Fincident which has tragically resulted
OL,13,Fin one woman losing her life and
OL,14,Fanother man in hospital with injuries.
OL,16,F"Our thoughts at this time are with
OL,17,Fboth victims and their loved ones, who
OL,18,Fare being supported by specialist
OL,19,Fofficers.
OL,26,@sD@OOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/5
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1784033311
OL,3,CMan arrested over murder of 24-year-
OL,4,Cold woman in double stabbing
OL,6,F"Our enquiries are in the early stages
OL,7,Fbut we do not believe there to be any
OL,8,Fwider threat to the public.
OL,10,F"However, we are keen to hear from
OL,11,Fanyone who may have seen anything or
OL,12,Fwho has any information that could
OL,13,Fassist our investigation.
OL,15,F"We know this incident will have
OL,16,Fcaused significant concern in the
OL,17,Fcommunity and residents can expect to
OL,18,Fsee an increased police presence in
OL,19,Fthe area over the coming days."
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUwD@AOU{D@_O]
